detailed_optimizations.code_changes:
将内层循环分块以改善缓存局部性。将j循环分成大小为B的块，确保在计算每个块时，所需的数据能保留在L1缓存中。

for (t = 0; t <= _PB_TSTEPS - 1; t++)
  for (i = 1; i <= _PB_N - 2; i++)
    for (jj = 1; jj <= _PB_N - 2; jj += B)
      for (j = jj; j <= min(jj+B-1, _PB_N-2); j++)
        A[i][j] = (A[i-1][j-1] + A[i-1][j] + A[i-1][j+1]
                   + A[i][j-1] + A[i][j] + A[i][j+1]
                   + A[i+1][j-1] + A[i+1][j] + A[i+1][j+1])/SCALAR_VAL(9.0);

合并多个时间步以减少数据访问次数。对于每个网格点，一次性计算多个时间步，使用临时变量存储中间结果。

for (t = 0; t <= _PB_TSTEPS - 1; t += K) {
  for (i = 1; i <= _PB_N - 2; i++) {
    for (j = 1; j <= _PB_N - 2; j++) {
      DATA_TYPE temp = A[i][j];
      for (k = 0; k < K && t+k <= _PB_TSTEPS-1; k++) {
        temp = (A[i-1][j-1] + A[i-1][j] + A[i-1][j+1]
                + A[i][j-1] + temp + A[i][j+1]
                + A[i+1][j-1] + A[i+1][j] + A[i+1][j+1])/SCALAR_VAL(9.0);
      }
      A[i][j] = temp;
    }
  }
}

将二维数组转换为一维数组并采用行优先存储，改善内存访问模式。

DATA_TYPE* A_flat = (DATA_TYPE*)malloc(n * n * sizeof(DATA_TYPE));
// 在计算中通过A_flat[i*n + j]访问元素
for (t = 0; t <= _PB_TSTEPS - 1; t++)
  for (i = 1; i <= _PB_N - 2; i++)
    for (j = 1; j <= _PB_N - 2; j++)
      A_flat[i*n + j] = (A_flat[(i-1)*n + (j-1)] + A_flat[(i-1)*n + j] + A_flat[(i-1)*n + (j+1)]
                         + A_flat[i*n + (j-1)] + A_flat[i*n + j] + A_flat[i*n + (j+1)]
                         + A_flat[(i+1)*n + (j-1)] + A_flat[(i+1)*n + j] + A_flat[(i+1)*n + (j+1)])/SCALAR_VAL(9.0);
